            "headline": "LDRA supports MISRA C:2025, aiding safety-critical systems' compliance. Developers can now benefit from the updated guidelines for faster market time.",
            "id": "bec7f3b1-51e5-4a93-a9ef-3a52a7f05ec6",
            "is_major": false,
            "source": "Business Wire",
            "source_type": "news",
            "summary": "In Wirral, England, LDRA has been a leader in MISRA C standards for many years. They have recently announced their support for the latest version, MISRA C:2025, issued by the MISRA C Working Group. With this update, developers can benefit from new guidelines, policy adjustments, and improvements facilitated by LDRA's automated static code analysis and reporting features. This support allows for quicker compliance and smoother processes, ultimately leading to faster product launches with improved quality.",
